30.24	Lee_Majors	Lee Majors	Lee Majors (born April 23, 1939) is an American television, film and voice actor, best known for his roles as Heath Barkley in the TV series The Big Valley (1965 - 1969), as Colonel Steve Austin in The Six Million Dollar Man (1973–1978) and as Colt Seavers in The Fall Guy (1981–1986).	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/2c/Lee_Majors_at_Baftas.02.jpg/220px-Lee_Majors_at_Baftas.02.jpg
